citeinfo.title: Walkways on the University of Idaho Campus Moscow, Idaho

idinfo.native: Microsoft Windows 2000 Version 5.2 (Build 3790) Service Pack 2; ESRI ArcCatalog 9.3.1.3000

descript.abstract: This data set portrays walkways located on the University of Idaho Campus Moscow, Idaho as of 2005. A special permit is required by anyone wishing to drive a motor vehicle is driven on these walkways.
descript.purpose: This dataset is intended for use by Facilities Services for producing maps and managing assets of the University of Idaho. These data are provided to the public primarily for use by University of Idaho students to aid in the completion of course projects. However, these data are not being updated on a regular basis and are current only to 2005. No responsibility is assumed by the University of Idaho in the use of these data.

procstep.procdesc: Dataset copied from University of Idaho Facilities Services server.

Dataset projection definition did not exist. ArcToolbox was used to define the projection by importing the parameters from another dataset in the same folder. The dataset that the projection parameters were imported from was: R:\GIS\proj\parking\parking.

The original ArcInfo coverage was loaded into an ArcSDE 9.2 Geodatabase. Some attributes from the original dataset were not imported. The dataset was projected from State Plane East NAD27 to State Plane West NAD83 using the NADCON Transformation. Metadata was created.
